Class RestServletGroupDefault

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ResourceGroup

    @RestResource
public abstract class RestServletGroupDefault
extends RestServletDefault
    Specialized subclass of RestServletDefault for showing "group" pages.

    Group pages consist of simple lists of child resource URLs and their labels. They're meant to be used as jumping-off points for child resources.

    Child resources are specified using the RestResource.children() annotation.

    Author:
    James Bognar (james.bognar@salesforce.com)
